    public abstract class Cinema
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISerializable
    A hall in a cineplex that screens movies. Contains showtimes that indicate what movie is screening at any given point in time.

      • printSeatingPlan

        public void printSeatingPlan​(Showtime showtime)
        Prints the current seating plan of a cinema at a given showtime. Prints seating in alphanumerical format. Letter stands for Row, Number stands for Column. Available seats are printed as "(__)" while booked seats are printed as "(xx)";
        Parameters:
        showtime - Showtime given for query.
